Review and Rating Management Module
The Review and Rating Management Module allows customers to leave feedback on products they’ve purchased, helping other customers make informed decisions and giving businesses insight into product quality and customer satisfaction.

📋 Features
1. Add a Review/Rating
Customers add a review and rating (1 to 5 stars) for purchased products.

Supports text reviews up to 1000 characters.

2. Review Moderation
Admins moderate reviews, approving or rejecting them based on quality and guidelines.

3. View Product Reviews
Customers see approved reviews and ratings on each product’s page.

4. Delete/Update Reviews
Admins can delete inappropriate reviews.

Customers can update or delete their own reviews.

🗄️ Database Design
Table Name: reviews

Column Name	Data Type	Description
review_id	INT, PK, AUTO_INCREMENT	Unique identifier for each review
product_id	INT, FK	References products(product_id)
customer_id	INT, FK	References users(user_id)
rating	INT	Rating (1-5 stars)
review_text	VARCHAR(1000)	Customer’s review content
created_at	DATETIME	Review creation timestamp
updated_at	DATETIME	Last updated timestamp
status	BOOLEAN	True for approved, False for unapproved
SQL Script:

sql
CREATE TABLE reviews (
  review_id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_id INT,
  customer_id INT,
  rating INT CHECK (rating >= 1 AND rating <= 5),
  review_text VARCHAR(1000),
  created_at DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  updated_at DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  status BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
  FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES users(user_id)
);
